'''Mugodhi''' (''Mine'' in English) imhando ye[[hushangazhi]] hunochera matombo akakosha kubva muvhu, nokukorora simbi kubuda mumatombo anenge acherwa. Matombo aya anogona kunge aine simbi dzakakosha kana kuti achishandiswa mune mamwe mabasa anowanikwa muhushangazhi. 

*Munyika yeZimbabwe tine migodhi inochera simbi dzakakosha dzinoti: gold; platiunum; chrome uye lithium. 

*Kunoitawo migodhi inochera mamwe matombo asiri esimbi anoti: diamond; limestone; magnesium uye silicates.

*Matombo ane simbi yakakosha anodanwa kunzi [[chitofu]] - (ore in English).

*Matombo asina simbi yakakosha anodanwa kunzi [[mambara]] - (waste rock in English)

